Subject: [PATCH v1 2/3] Bluetooth: btmtkuart: fix recv_buf() return value
Date: Mon, 27 Nov 2023 20:14:07 +0100
Message-Id: <20231127191409.151254-3-francesco@dolcini.it>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.25.1
